_sText:
This is a GunGame (deathmatch) map, desinged like a Alien Spaceship. I used many Teslas. And spot_lights. There is also a difficult secret in the map, which makes you invincible. Good luck to find it. But if you know it, don´´t use it all the time when this map is on a server, because then it is getting boring. 


Hope you will enjoy it and please rate it. 


MAP BY Da_Flippo
